sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Browser
    participant MM as media-manager
    participant VM as video-manager
    participant FF as FFmpeg
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant FS as Filesystem

    C->>MM: POST /api/media/upload (multipart)
    MM->>FS: write temp file
    MM->>DB: insert media_item (status=processing)
    MM-->>C: 202 Accepted + slug

    C->>VM: WS /api/media/{slug}/progress/ws

    MM->>VM: spawn tokio task process_video()
    Note over VM: Stage 1: Validate
    Note over VM: Stage 2: Extract metadata (ffprobe)
    Note over VM: Stage 3: Transcode HLS (ffmpeg)
    VM->>FF: subprocess (1080p/720p/480p/360p)
    FF-->>VM: HLS segments + playlists
    VM-->>C: progress updates (25–85%)
    Note over VM: Stage 4: Generate thumbnail
    Note over VM: Stage 5: Generate poster
    VM->>DB: update media_item (status=active)
    VM->>FS: storage/vaults/{vault_id}/media/videos/{slug}/
    VM-->>C: 100% complete

    C->>MM: GET /media/{slug}/thumbnail
    MM->>FS: storage/vaults/{vault_id}/thumbnails/videos/{slug}_thumb.webp
    FS-->>C: WebP thumbnail
